{"tid":1538432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[十萬火急!!!] 如果佢話撤回 我地就全世界收皮!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:08:54.000Z","uid":69485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e22fb6fb90a8b305967f39d43c27b5e5bc3b8be2","tid":1538432,"uid":69485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我最擔憂既畫面終於出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月呢風波 傳媒同我地都統稱為 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">送中風波</span></strong><br />\n無錯 事源係送中條例 百萬人上街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYJRmve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYJRmve.jpg&h=40667cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">然後 <strong>我地有手足犧牲...</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdcntai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjdcntai.jpg&h=e36e59f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後 <strong>力度慢慢升級 政府堅持</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>然後 <strong>721</strong> (我屌你老母)</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ovxbmvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvxbmvm.jpg&h=9e320c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後 直至今日為止 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtUEvoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtUEvoM.jpg&h=94c1bf2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地無左幾多手足 人心有幾徬徨 <br />\n黑警有幾仆街 政府有幾漠視 <br />\n成個體制有幾不公...</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢一切話比我地知<br />\n個問題<br />\n係個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">制度</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一日唔FIX 好個制<br />\n過左呢件事件<br />\n<strong>仲有幾多人會日日關心時事</strong><br />\n會好留意<span style=\"color: red;\">行會</span>既小動作<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政黨</span>既假動作<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span>既滲透<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">義士提堂呢 支持香港既小店呢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班HIGH HIGH 未又係去番食吉野家我屌</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKgfOaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKgfOaA.jpg&h=084438fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家番工既番工 打機既打機 <br />\n睇劇行街食飯去旅行買唔起樓自由行落番黎MPF繼續蝕黑警繼續食長糧</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母<br />\n清醒D啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當初點解要係咁叫呢個口號<br />\n點解係缺一不可<br />\n有人叫香港人加油既時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你聽唔到總會有人屌你叫番五大訴求咩!</span><br />\n你唔發現<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 泛民班仆街好撚少打明五大訴求咩!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自己香港自己救</span></strong></span><br />\n只有集結成浪潮 我地先夠力量<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若然此時話袋住先 你地同散水撚無分別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mnbzjhi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnbzjhi.jpg&h=61d611e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n樓下寫左WHY 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我SHARE 呀!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E7%BC%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8